&lt;p&gt;And &lt;a href="http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.5/en/miscellaneous-functions.html#function_inet-aton" rel="noreferrer"&gt;&lt;code&gt;INET_ATON&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.5/en/miscellaneous-functions.html#function_inet-ntoa" rel="noreferrer"&gt;&lt;code&gt;INET_NTOA&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to convert them:&lt;/p&gt;

